sequenceDiagram
    participant JS as JS (H5 页面)
    participant Bridge as JSBridge SDK
    participant WV as WebView (Native)
    participant Handler as BridgeHandler

    Note over JS, Handler: 方式一：@JavascriptInterface
    JS->>Bridge: JSBridge.call("user", "getInfo", params, callback)
    Bridge->>Bridge: 生成 callbackId, 存入 callbacks Map
    Bridge->>WV: window.NativeBridge.dispatch(JSON)
    Note right of WV: WebKit 线程调用
    WV->>Handler: dispatch(module, method, params)
    Handler-->>WV: callback(response)
    WV->>Bridge: evaluateJavascript("JSBridge.onCallback(id, data)")
    Bridge->>JS: 执行 callback(response)

    Note over JS, Handler: 方式二：URL Scheme 拦截
    JS->>WV: iframe.src = "jsbridge://method?params=..."
    WV->>WV: shouldOverrideUrlLoading 拦截
    WV->>Handler: 解析 URL, dispatch
    Handler-->>WV: callback(response)
    WV->>JS: evaluateJavascript 回传结果

    Note over JS, Handler: 方式三：WebMessagePort 双向通道
    WV->>JS: postWebMessage(init, [jsPort])
    JS->>JS: 保存 port 引用
    JS->>WV: port.postMessage("request")
    WV->>Handler: onMessage 分发处理
    Handler-->>WV: nativePort.postMessage("response")
    WV->>JS: port.onmessage 接收
